      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>Please tell me what you've seen there….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Priestess of Darkness Madeleine listens to you)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
