   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-b" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>That used to be a place where the corrupted Ancients created evil life forms. What you have seen befits the end for someone who has created an uncontrollable monster.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Priestess of Darkness Madeleine smiles slightly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-c" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>Anyway, I got the answer for the second riddle as well.<BR>Empty for fools but full for the wise.<BR>The answer was <FONT color=#a82424>regrets</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-d" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why are you solving these riddles?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>Fools never know what they have done wrong even if they had done something terrible.<BR>Wise ones will realize it even if it may be a little too late. I wish they knew what they were doing was wrong before they even started regretting.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-e" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Priestess of Darkness Madeleine seems to be smiling)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>As I have told you, it's just a pastime for me.<BR>I've been here for too long.<BR>Boredom can sometimes be worse than death.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-2-f" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>To me, time runs forever, and there also are boundless number of riddles that I have to solve.<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, if it's alright with you, would you help me in solving one more riddle?</html>]]></talk_question>
